# AI Placement Advisor

AI Placement Advisor is a ServiceNow-based application that helps students identify suitable placement opportunities based on their skills and receive AI-powered career guidance using Gemini AI.

## Project Overview

Traditional placement systems mainly store candidate and job data. This project improves that process by adding automated skill matching, missing skill detection, match score calculation, AI-based career advice, dashboards, and role-based security.

## Modules

### Candidate Profile

Stores candidate details such as name, branch, CGPA, email, resume, and mapped ServiceNow user.

### Skill Inventory

Stores candidate skills such as Python, SQL, Power BI, Java, Communication, and other technical skills.

### Opportunity Catalog

Stores company opportunities with job role, required skills, minimum CGPA, and eligible branch.

### Career Match Results

Stores generated recommendations including match score, missing skills, recommendation status, and AI advice.

